      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Terrific race but hard to go past ZOUSTROLOGY (6) who is unbeaten here, scoring with ease at the last two starts, the latest by 5.5 lengths. Has speed and is the one to run down. ROBRICK (2) placed in a Class 3 fresh then was midfield last time in a tougher race. Well placed here third-up and gets a chance to improve. BRAVEHEART (1) was runner-up in a Class 3 two back then placed in a Class 4 latest. Continues to race well and is among the chances. SWAG (9) is a handy galloper resuming who has placed 3/3 fresh. Has a low draw and did place at only try course and distance. Expected to run well fresh.",
